    <div class="container">
        <div class="page-header">
            <h1>Welcome to VizMyGrant.</h1>
            <p>We have cleaned and collated grants related data from <a href="https://www.nhmrc.gov.au/grants/outcomes-funding-rounds">NHMRC</a> and provided a few ways to visualise the data for your pleasure.</p>
            <div class="row">
              <a href="https://viz-my-grant.shinyapps.io/view/">
                <div class="col-md-1">
                  <image class="img-responsive" src="images/VariableRelationships.png" alt="Relationships Between Variables"></image>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-2">Explore the funding landscape in 2014 by examining relationships between variables in an interactive plot.</div>
              </a>
              <div class="col-md-1">&nbsp;</div>
              <a href="Circles.html">
                <div class="col-md-1">
                  <image class="img-responsive" src="images/Circles.png" alt="Circles View"></image>
