                <div class="col-md-2">Explore the level of funding through circles that represent the break down of funding across different categories.</div>
              </a>
              <div class="col-md-1">&nbsp;</div>
              <a href="https://public.tableausoftware.com/views/VizMyGrant/Dashboard?:embed=y&:display_count=no">
                <div class="col-md-1">
                  <image class="img-responsive" src="images/Tableau.png" alt="Tableau Visualisations"></image>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-2">Varying views of the data through the powerful Tableau tool.</div>
              </a>
              <div class="col-md-1">&nbsp;</div>            
            </div>
            <div class="row">  
              <a href="topography.html">
                <div class="col-md-1">
                  <image class="img-responsive" src="images/Topography.png" alt="Geographical Heatmap"></image>
